%div{ style: "font: normal 14px/1 Arial; color: #333" }
  %p= "Hello #{@resource.fullname}!"

  %p Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.

  %p= link_to "Change My Password", edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token)

  %p{ style: "color: #777" } If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
  %p{ style: "color: #777" } Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.